WEBVTT

01:43.240 --> 01:47.160
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:50.000 --> 01:53.280
XIGU ALLEY

02:03.720 --> 02:05.600
Zheng! Zheng!

02:05.680 --> 02:07.040
Changyu's slaughtering a pig!

02:07.120 --> 02:08.720
Hurry, come watch!

02:08.800 --> 02:10.000
Slaughtering a pig?

02:15.840 --> 02:17.920
Don't move. I'll make it quick for you.

02:18.600 --> 02:20.960
Be a good pig in this life.
Be a good person in the next!

02:23.040 --> 02:25.120
I've heard that somewhere before.

02:26.200 --> 02:27.560
Changyu's impressive, isn't she?

02:37.840 --> 02:38.960
Yan Zheng.

02:39.040 --> 02:41.720
Take Ning inside. Don't let her watch.

02:42.240 --> 02:43.920
Or she'll have nightmares again.

02:44.440 --> 02:45.600
Alright.

02:46.400 --> 02:47.280
Let's go.

03:08.480 --> 03:09.520
Don't look.

03:14.440 --> 03:15.680
Don't be afraid.

03:17.760 --> 03:18.920
I'm not afraid of that.

03:19.000 --> 03:21.480
I mean, don't be afraid of my sister.

03:46.320 --> 03:47.360
Do you need my help?

03:53.200 --> 03:55.960
Did I scare you just now?

03:58.280 --> 04:00.440
If you're scared or disgusted,
just say so.

04:00.520 --> 04:02.400
I'm used to it.

04:06.280 --> 04:07.120
Scared? Not really.

04:09.320 --> 04:10.640
Then you're disgusted.

04:17.560 --> 04:19.000
You never minded my injuries.

04:19.720 --> 04:21.720
How could I mind the work you do?

04:36.400 --> 04:38.000
Stop staring. Go back inside.

04:41.880 --> 04:44.160
Go inside and rest. Leave the fire to me.

04:44.240 --> 04:45.960
Once we start singeing
the bristles, it'll stink.

04:46.640 --> 04:47.760
That's nothing.

04:47.840 --> 04:49.640
I've smelled worse.

04:50.160 --> 04:51.320
Burning corpses.

04:54.040 --> 04:54.960
Right.

04:55.480 --> 04:56.920
You worked as an escort guard.

04:57.560 --> 04:58.760
You must have seen the dead.

05:39.040 --> 05:40.160
This pork…

05:40.240 --> 05:41.600
Should I hang it up?

05:42.640 --> 05:43.880
Not yet.

05:44.400 --> 05:46.160
This pork

05:46.240 --> 05:47.400
needs to be cured with salt.

05:47.480 --> 05:50.440
Just like this.
Spread the salt evenly on the meat.

05:51.080 --> 05:52.120
Salt it for a few days,
then hang it to dry.

06:00.600 --> 06:02.880
Let me do it. I'll help you.

06:19.480 --> 06:21.600
My parents used to make
cured meat like this,

06:21.680 --> 06:22.520
working together.

06:23.560 --> 06:24.800
Then what did you do?

06:26.040 --> 06:27.720
Ning and I only caused trouble.

06:37.800 --> 06:39.880
This piece is still too big.

06:40.600 --> 06:42.040
Make cuts so the flavor gets in.

06:42.640 --> 06:44.160
Pass me the knife.

07:10.560 --> 07:11.600
This one.

07:13.960 --> 07:14.920
This knife…

07:15.440 --> 07:16.800
Where did it come from?

07:17.600 --> 07:18.920
My father had it specially forged.

07:19.680 --> 07:22.480
Do you know what this knife was made of?

07:23.080 --> 07:24.280
Iron.

07:24.880 --> 07:26.080
What did you expect, silver?

07:27.240 --> 07:28.640
But Father said

07:29.240 --> 07:31.880
these two knives are our heirlooms.

07:31.960 --> 07:33.480
They fed our whole family.

07:38.240 --> 07:39.520
Seems his skills were good.

07:39.600 --> 07:40.880
Where did he learn?

07:41.480 --> 07:43.720
He roamed far and wide in his youth.

07:43.800 --> 07:45.880
He probably learned
from some reclusive master.

08:09.360 --> 08:10.680
BY IMPERIAL GRACE

08:24.320 --> 08:25.160
You win.

08:26.600 --> 08:28.280
Uncle, I win!

08:35.880 --> 08:37.360
It's only a slight edge.

08:37.440 --> 08:39.360
Is that worth celebrating?

08:39.960 --> 08:42.799
That's General He humoring you.

08:51.160 --> 08:52.000
No…

08:54.960 --> 08:56.680
Salt is expensive.

08:57.640 --> 09:00.280
It's just a little salt.
What's there to fuss about?

09:01.200 --> 09:02.960
You don't manage the household,
so you don't know.

09:08.840 --> 09:11.320
Changyu, is the pig's tail ready?

09:13.240 --> 09:15.640
It's in the pot. It needs a bit more time.

09:15.720 --> 09:16.560
Look at you.

09:19.080 --> 09:21.440
It's not even ready,
and you're already drooling.

09:22.320 --> 09:23.640
Little glutton.

09:23.720 --> 09:26.560
-I'm not a glutton!
-You are.

09:30.280 --> 09:31.280
Got it!

09:54.840 --> 09:56.000
What are you…

09:56.680 --> 09:58.560
I've seen this gyrfalcon around
a few times.

09:58.640 --> 10:00.160
So I set a trap for it.

10:00.240 --> 10:01.520
Didn't think I'd actually catch it.

10:04.960 --> 10:06.640
You little brute, you dare bite me?

10:07.800 --> 10:10.520
I'll take it to the market tomorrow
and sell it for ten taels.

10:10.600 --> 10:12.080
At the market…

10:12.160 --> 10:14.120
Few people buy live birds like this.

10:14.720 --> 10:15.760
Not many know how to tame one.

10:15.840 --> 10:17.880
Its wild nature is hard to break.

10:17.960 --> 10:18.800
It could easily hurt someone.

10:19.720 --> 10:20.800
That's a pity.

10:21.520 --> 10:23.000
Its wing's injured too.

10:23.960 --> 10:24.800
Otherwise,

10:25.520 --> 10:27.440
I'll just stew it for soup.

10:28.120 --> 10:29.160
Ning, turn around.

10:29.960 --> 10:31.080
No.

10:34.280 --> 10:35.600
I have eaten

10:36.120 --> 10:37.600
this kind of bird before.

10:38.120 --> 10:40.200
Tough and gamey. Barely edible.

10:42.240 --> 10:44.280
Don't worry, I'll prepare it.

10:44.360 --> 10:46.160
My braising stock could
make even wood taste good.

10:46.720 --> 10:47.960
No.

10:52.640 --> 10:55.200
Actually, I know a bit about taming birds.

10:55.800 --> 10:57.120
I can try to tame it.

10:57.720 --> 11:00.560
A trained gyrfalcon can fetch
over a hundred taels.

11:02.480 --> 11:03.320
Over a hundred taels?

11:07.480 --> 11:08.920
That's far too expensive!

11:09.600 --> 11:11.640
-Ning, get a chicken cage.
-All right.

11:12.960 --> 11:14.760
Then we'll keep you at home for now.

11:14.840 --> 11:16.240
My little hundred-tael prize.

11:24.560 --> 11:25.640
You foolish bird.

11:43.800 --> 11:44.920
What are you doing?

11:46.920 --> 11:47.920
I'm bandaging it.

11:49.160 --> 11:50.760
Why are you using that?

11:53.760 --> 11:55.760
What's wrong with this strip of cloth?

11:56.800 --> 11:58.320
This is the hair ribbon I gave you.

12:03.000 --> 12:04.960
I thought it was just a rag.

12:14.320 --> 12:16.280
Father, Mother,
as the year draws to a close…

12:17.840 --> 12:19.160
this is our New Year pig.

12:19.240 --> 12:20.480
I brought some for you to try.

12:24.960 --> 12:26.600
It's only the third day since my wedding.

12:28.040 --> 12:29.520
My husband doesn't know

12:29.600 --> 12:30.720
we must be frugal with salt.

12:32.440 --> 12:34.200
But he helped me make cured meat.

12:34.920 --> 12:36.520
And he stands up to support me.

12:40.160 --> 12:41.720
Father, Mother, please bless him

12:42.880 --> 12:46.440
with a swift recovery
and a peaceful life ahead.

12:52.760 --> 12:53.760
As for Song Yan…

12:59.440 --> 13:00.520
that wretched schemer…

13:01.600 --> 13:03.040
make him fail the imperial exams!

13:10.840 --> 13:13.120
SPIRIT TABLET OF MENG LIHUA
SPIRIT TABLET OF FAN ERNIU

13:15.080 --> 13:16.680
TEA

13:16.760 --> 13:19.000
TEA, NOODLE SOUP, FAN'S PORK STALL

13:19.080 --> 13:20.560
DUMPLINGS, GUO'S PORK STALL, NOODLE SOUP

13:20.640 --> 13:22.440
DUMPLINGS, GUO'S PORK STALL, NOODLE SOUP

13:25.640 --> 13:28.040
FAN'S PORK STALL

13:29.840 --> 13:31.840
Come take a look!

13:44.760 --> 13:48.000
FAN'S PORK STALL

13:48.800 --> 13:51.040
Who smashed my stall?

13:51.920 --> 13:54.480
If you've got the guts, show yourself!

13:55.000 --> 13:57.200
Whoever's hiding is a spineless bastard!

13:59.320 --> 14:02.160
Why are you staring at me? It wasn't me.

14:03.120 --> 14:04.520
You know what?

14:04.600 --> 14:07.640
When someone behaves recklessly,
Heaven will deal with her.

14:09.840 --> 14:11.280
Oh no, Changyu.

14:11.360 --> 14:14.040
Your stall's been shut
for nearly two months.

14:14.120 --> 14:15.520
Did you pay the protection fee?

14:16.600 --> 14:17.800
What protection fee?

14:22.960 --> 14:25.320
GUO'S PORK STALL, NOODLE SOUP

14:27.400 --> 14:29.560
GUO'S PORK STALL

14:31.560 --> 14:33.000
You still dare reopen?

14:33.880 --> 14:35.360
Not afraid of dying?

14:35.440 --> 14:38.200
Let's see who on this street

14:38.280 --> 14:39.480
dares refuse to pay.

14:41.560 --> 14:42.640
It's you.

14:43.320 --> 14:44.880
Turn around.

14:44.960 --> 14:46.200
I'm talking to you.

14:52.360 --> 14:54.440
Mrs. Fan…

14:58.880 --> 14:59.840
Oh.

14:59.920 --> 15:02.800
This… This pork stall is yours?

15:02.880 --> 15:03.720
Very good.

15:04.640 --> 15:05.480
How much are you asking for?

15:05.560 --> 15:07.840
A misunderstanding.
It's all a misunderstanding!

15:08.440 --> 15:09.840
How could we possibly
demand money from you?

15:10.360 --> 15:11.280
Hey!

15:17.720 --> 15:19.960
Understood. Fix it at once.

15:20.560 --> 15:21.480
Come on! Come on!

15:25.160 --> 15:27.400
We take money
to settle troubles for people.

15:28.560 --> 15:30.440
-Please forgive us.
-On whose behalf?

15:34.080 --> 15:36.040
We'll fix your stove.
Just don't ask, okay?

15:37.080 --> 15:38.080
We may be ruffians,

15:38.160 --> 15:40.120
but we don't betray our employers.

15:42.280 --> 15:43.240
Quite principled.

15:49.400 --> 15:50.840
The owner of Wang's Braised Meats sent us.

15:51.360 --> 15:52.520
Him?

15:54.480 --> 15:55.480
I don't even know him.

15:56.120 --> 15:57.080
I swear it.

15:59.640 --> 16:02.680
-You're called Mr. Jin, right?
-I am Jin Yuanbao.

16:02.760 --> 16:04.640
Just call me Yuanbao. Or Bao.

16:05.160 --> 16:07.960
Don't just tidy up here.
Inside needs tidying up too. Hurry up.

16:09.480 --> 16:11.640
They are Man Di, Man Cang, and Man Wu.

16:12.440 --> 16:14.640
-Order us as you please.
-All surnamed Man?

16:14.720 --> 16:17.080
I named them. Am I not called Jin Yuanbao?

16:17.160 --> 16:19.120
They should be Full House,
Ground, and Granary.

16:19.200 --> 16:21.280
Hurry and fix it. I need to reopen.

16:22.200 --> 16:24.120
-Open for business.
-Open for business.

16:24.200 --> 16:25.320
-You, come here.
-Come.

16:25.400 --> 16:26.640
-Come and buy meat.
-You, you…

16:28.440 --> 16:30.080
You two, come here.

16:30.160 --> 16:32.480
What are you doing? Forcing customers?

16:36.040 --> 16:38.320
Buy… Buy some pork!

16:38.400 --> 16:39.280
No, no.

16:40.040 --> 16:42.480
-Buy some!
-Go buy some meat!

16:42.560 --> 16:43.520
Come on. Come on.

16:43.600 --> 16:44.520
-Come on.
-Buy some.

16:44.600 --> 16:46.200
Come.

16:46.280 --> 16:48.120
FAN'S PORK STALL

16:49.440 --> 16:51.000
Just under three liang.

16:51.080 --> 16:52.000
Here you go.

16:52.080 --> 16:54.640
Pork belly.
Perfect balance of lean and fat!

16:55.280 --> 16:56.240
Any cut you like!

17:02.560 --> 17:03.520
Madam…

17:09.440 --> 17:12.200
-This cut's perfect for dumplings.
-Delicious, right? Come again!

17:12.280 --> 17:14.400
GUO'S PORK STALL

17:14.480 --> 17:16.079
See that?

17:16.160 --> 17:17.839
That woman

17:18.359 --> 17:19.839
is using cheap tricks to lure customers.

17:20.640 --> 17:23.000
Are you jealous or envious?

17:23.079 --> 17:25.400
Mind your words,
or you'll face retribution.

17:26.119 --> 17:28.520
I neither steal nor rob.
What retribution would I fear?

17:29.120 --> 17:30.640
Keep an eye on your husband.

17:30.720 --> 17:32.880
Then you'd better watch your own stove.

17:32.960 --> 17:34.280
Or it might get smashed too!

17:38.760 --> 17:39.800
Not bad.

17:39.880 --> 17:41.400
Come again next time!

17:41.920 --> 17:43.640
Fresh pork!

17:44.960 --> 17:46.920
Fresh pork!

17:48.880 --> 17:50.240
You little brat!

17:50.760 --> 17:52.400
-I'll beat you, you little brat!
-Granny…

17:52.920 --> 17:54.240
-Granny!
-Granny!

17:54.320 --> 17:55.640
-What are you doing here?
-To beat you!

17:55.720 --> 17:57.360
-Why?
-You…

17:58.200 --> 17:59.800
You're collecting protection fees again.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.760
When will you ever change?

18:01.840 --> 18:03.600
I didn't! Ask them
if you don't believe me!

18:04.200 --> 18:06.760
What's that in your hand?
Isn't that money?

18:07.760 --> 18:09.840
No, I… It's money,
but it's not protection money.

18:13.360 --> 18:15.720
The Fan sisters just lost their parents.

18:15.800 --> 18:17.680
Only the two of them remain. It's pitiful.

18:18.440 --> 18:20.520
Don't do such wicked things!

18:21.160 --> 18:22.240
You…

18:22.320 --> 18:24.880
-Don't do such wicked things!
-Granny, stop hitting!

18:24.960 --> 18:26.000
You don't know the situation.

18:26.840 --> 18:29.040
-You never listen!
-Granny, stop hitting!

18:29.120 --> 18:30.080
Granny Jin.

18:30.760 --> 18:32.040
He didn't take any money from me.

18:32.880 --> 18:35.360
They're helping me sell pork. Honest work.

18:42.080 --> 18:43.240
Selling pork?

18:44.440 --> 18:45.480
Is…

18:46.480 --> 18:47.360
Is that true?

18:48.520 --> 18:49.400
Yes.

18:50.160 --> 18:52.720
-They even swept the floor.
-We did.

18:52.800 --> 18:55.560
They also fixed the stove outside.

18:57.680 --> 18:59.640
Everyone saw, right?

19:01.040 --> 19:02.320
In a way.

19:09.560 --> 19:12.240
My grandson has potential.

19:14.120 --> 19:17.400
He used to be obedient and sensible.

19:20.040 --> 19:23.360
From now on, work steadily and honestly.

19:23.440 --> 19:25.680
Don't hold up Mrs. Fan's business.

19:25.760 --> 19:27.520
Granny, you hurry home.

19:27.600 --> 19:29.280
You're holding up business.

19:29.360 --> 19:31.200
-Okay.
-Go home.

19:32.760 --> 19:33.600
I…

19:37.320 --> 19:39.160
Look at you, child.

19:39.240 --> 19:40.520
Work hard.

19:48.080 --> 19:49.960
My grandson has potential.

19:50.720 --> 19:53.400
He won't do bad things again.

20:01.360 --> 20:02.440
Alright, alright.

20:06.280 --> 20:08.000
It's just my granny.

20:08.080 --> 20:10.080
I'm grown up, yet she still
treats me like a kid.

20:10.600 --> 20:12.640
If word gets out, how am I
supposed to keep my standing?

20:14.640 --> 20:16.400
Stop looking! Come and buy meat, quickly.

20:16.480 --> 20:18.080
If not, get lost.

20:18.160 --> 20:19.080
Come on, let's go.

20:19.720 --> 20:21.240
Take a look.

20:21.320 --> 20:23.520
You have such a good grandmother.

20:23.600 --> 20:24.440
Be content.

20:24.520 --> 20:25.760
You've got hands and feet.

20:26.280 --> 20:28.040
Earn an honest living.

20:29.480 --> 20:31.880
What honest work could we even do?

20:32.960 --> 20:33.800
In times like these,

20:34.880 --> 20:36.840
it's hard enough to survive as a rogue,
let alone as a good man.

20:37.720 --> 20:40.400
Man Wu's mother
is sick and needs medicine.

20:42.040 --> 20:43.560
Man Di's sister

20:43.640 --> 20:45.800
was forced by her uncle
to work at Huaman House.

20:45.880 --> 20:46.760
In half a year, she'll turn 15.

20:47.360 --> 20:49.400
If she's not redeemed,
she'll be registered as a courtesan.

20:55.040 --> 20:56.000
Man Cang

20:56.920 --> 20:57.960
has been an orphan.

20:58.560 --> 21:00.120
He eats a lot, but isn't very bright.

21:00.200 --> 21:01.760
He can't handle proper work.
Who would hire him?

21:03.640 --> 21:05.440
We do want to be good people.

21:06.280 --> 21:07.880
But in these years of endless war,

21:09.320 --> 21:10.480
good people can barely survive.

21:18.400 --> 21:19.680
This is half fat, half lean.

21:19.760 --> 21:20.920
Perfect for dumplings.

21:21.000 --> 21:22.320
Thirty-five coins per jin.

21:22.400 --> 21:25.080
It's a little over two jin.
Let's just count it as two.

21:25.160 --> 21:26.920
Alright, I'll weigh it for you.

21:27.000 --> 21:28.000
There's more here.

21:28.840 --> 21:30.200
Take care. Come again next time.

21:30.800 --> 21:32.240
Fresh pork!

22:14.760 --> 22:17.080
Eat. This is for men who work honestly.

22:17.160 --> 22:18.000
Not poisoned.

22:41.920 --> 22:43.160
This is today's wages.

22:43.240 --> 22:45.520
You only worked half a day,
so you get half a day's pay.

22:46.440 --> 22:47.640
I won't give more.

22:47.720 --> 22:49.040
But I won't short you either.

23:00.520 --> 23:02.880
Slow down. You're not on the gallows.

23:06.240 --> 23:07.360
Mrs. Fan.

23:12.560 --> 23:13.400
Well…

23:14.360 --> 23:16.200
Can we still come to help in the future?

23:22.280 --> 23:25.160
Short on food and willing to work?
You're welcome here.

23:25.240 --> 23:27.160
But if you do wrong, I won't show mercy.

23:42.680 --> 23:44.240
It's Wang's shop on Central Street, right?

23:45.720 --> 23:46.560
Yes.

23:49.680 --> 23:50.680
You're going for revenge?

23:51.640 --> 23:52.600
Mrs. Yin.

23:52.680 --> 23:55.120
Please look after the shop for me.
Thank you.

23:57.280 --> 23:58.160
Okay.

24:05.680 --> 24:07.120
A man must have loyalty.

24:07.200 --> 24:08.120
Let's go.

24:12.760 --> 24:15.880
No wonder those ruffians obey her.

24:16.960 --> 24:19.000
She's the real boss of them!

24:19.880 --> 24:21.080
Sir.

24:21.160 --> 24:22.240
All this money

24:22.320 --> 24:24.280
for rice, flour, salt,
oil, soy sauce, and vinegar?

24:25.360 --> 24:26.560
One cart won't be enough to carry it all.

24:27.160 --> 24:28.320
Then prepare another cart.

24:28.920 --> 24:29.760
Alright!

24:29.840 --> 24:32.600
Add ten more jars of fine wine,
suitable for elders.

24:33.680 --> 24:35.280
Add some tea leaves and pastries as well.

24:35.360 --> 24:36.200
This is the address.

24:36.280 --> 24:37.280
No problem.

24:40.920 --> 24:42.160
Right.

24:42.240 --> 24:44.680
Do you have any ointment
suitable for chapped skin?

24:45.360 --> 24:46.320
Yes, we do.

24:47.320 --> 24:50.000
We have the best clam ointment.

24:52.120 --> 24:54.200
Just arrived. Take a look.

24:58.560 --> 24:59.400
I'll take them all.

25:01.640 --> 25:02.680
Certainly, sir.

25:05.320 --> 25:07.640
Where can I buy wrist guards like these?

25:08.760 --> 25:10.160
Do you have any for young ladies?

25:10.920 --> 25:12.160
Sir, you must be joking.

25:12.720 --> 25:15.320
We men wear these wrist guards

25:15.920 --> 25:17.080
for heavy labor.

25:17.160 --> 25:19.280
They are not for young ladies.

25:19.880 --> 25:21.040
You won't find any.

25:23.400 --> 25:25.240
Where is Mrs. Fan going?

25:26.000 --> 25:27.240
She looks furious.

25:27.760 --> 25:29.320
She's going to settle the score.

25:32.960 --> 25:33.960
What's going on?

25:34.040 --> 25:35.040
Haven't you heard?

25:35.120 --> 25:37.200
Wang is jealous of her business.

25:37.280 --> 25:39.560
He sent men to smash her stall.

25:39.640 --> 25:41.880
So she's heading to Wang's with her men.

25:42.760 --> 25:44.240
If anyone asks,

25:44.320 --> 25:46.520
just say Fan Erniu placed an order here

25:46.600 --> 25:48.400
and paid in advance for New Year goods.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.240
Alright, sir.

25:51.640 --> 25:52.840
Such a nice girl.

25:52.920 --> 25:55.440
How did she turn so fierce?
Don't you think so, sir?

25:56.440 --> 25:57.800
Thank you, sir.

26:00.760 --> 26:02.120
STEAMED STUFFED BUN

26:04.040 --> 26:05.600
Mrs. Fan, you're here today to--

26:06.440 --> 26:08.000
-Gentlemen…
-Step aside!

26:08.080 --> 26:08.920
WANG'S BRAISED MEATS

26:10.520 --> 26:12.080
Tell the owner to come out.

26:12.160 --> 26:13.840
He had the guts to smash my stall,

26:13.920 --> 26:15.440
now he hides like a turtle?

26:16.280 --> 26:17.400
What's going on?

26:18.000 --> 26:18.960
Gentlemen…

26:19.040 --> 26:20.840
Let's wait until our owner arrives.

26:21.440 --> 26:23.040
What's all the noise?

26:26.120 --> 26:26.960
Landlord.

26:35.440 --> 26:37.560
So you're the one
who sent men to smash my stall?

26:37.640 --> 26:38.520
It was him.

26:38.600 --> 26:41.560
He gave us five taels to smash your stove.

26:42.400 --> 26:43.240
Who are you?

26:43.320 --> 26:45.520
Trying to deny it
now that there's no proof?

26:45.600 --> 26:47.680
We were just drinking at the tavern.

26:47.760 --> 26:49.600
Weren't you the one who approached us?

26:49.680 --> 26:50.960
-And you still deny it?
-Exactly!

26:51.040 --> 26:53.080
The tavern owner can also testify to it.

26:53.160 --> 26:54.720
Anyone who goes back
on his word is a coward!

26:54.800 --> 26:56.600
The noble heir of the Wang family

26:56.680 --> 26:59.520
dares to smash a stall,
yet dares not admit it?

27:06.440 --> 27:08.280
It's just a stove.

27:08.920 --> 27:10.680
I smashed it. So what?

27:11.560 --> 27:12.720
What can you do to me?

27:14.840 --> 27:17.000
A girl like you

27:17.080 --> 27:19.440
should be in your chambers embroidering,

27:19.520 --> 27:22.360
yet you run out to do business.

27:22.440 --> 27:24.800
Isn't that absurd?

27:28.000 --> 27:29.840
Just because I'm a woman,

27:30.640 --> 27:31.920
I should endure your bullying?

27:33.400 --> 27:34.720
I'm not bullying you.

27:35.520 --> 27:38.000
I'm doing you a favor.

27:39.800 --> 27:40.800
Look at you.

27:41.600 --> 27:43.520
You are rather pretty.

27:44.040 --> 27:47.840
Why toil so hard for such petty trade?

27:50.440 --> 27:51.800
I have plenty of silver.

27:56.440 --> 27:57.360
Name your price.

27:58.320 --> 28:02.240
Sell me the recipe,
and yourself as well. How about it?

28:07.520 --> 28:09.360
What are you, to think you're worthy

28:10.040 --> 28:11.560
of buying my recipe?

28:17.160 --> 28:18.320
You wretch.

28:19.040 --> 28:23.000
By cozying up to that old dog Li Deqin,

28:23.080 --> 28:25.640
you stole our business
with Yixiang Restaurant!

28:25.720 --> 28:27.440
And you still dare show up?

28:27.520 --> 28:30.000
You pig-slaughtering wench, how dare you--

28:36.960 --> 28:38.560
-Yes!
-Yes!

28:41.400 --> 28:43.560
When she dealt with us before,

28:44.080 --> 28:45.520
she was holding back!

28:47.400 --> 28:48.360
Tell me.

28:48.880 --> 28:51.880
How did I steal your business
with Yixiang Restaurant?

28:52.480 --> 28:57.600
We… We lost Yixiang Restaurant's business.

28:57.680 --> 29:01.160
I heard Li Deqin recommended your pork.

29:02.560 --> 29:04.800
And because of that, you slander me?

29:06.280 --> 29:07.560
Sorry, sorry.

29:07.640 --> 29:09.080
-Serves him right!
-Yes!

29:09.160 --> 29:10.920
Good thing it's Fan Erniu's daughter.

29:11.000 --> 29:14.480
If it were some other family's children
being bullied like this,

29:14.560 --> 29:17.160
-they'd have nowhere to turn.
-But Heaven!

29:17.240 --> 29:18.400
That's right.

29:18.480 --> 29:21.360
To me,
this is Wang's bullying decent folk.

29:21.440 --> 29:22.280
Exactly!

29:22.360 --> 29:26.120
Back when the old owner was alive,
their business thrived.

29:26.200 --> 29:28.040
Ever since he passed away,

29:28.120 --> 29:30.280
their braised meat
has worsened by the day.

29:30.360 --> 29:31.200
-Right?
-Yeah!

29:31.880 --> 29:33.440
No wonder Yixiang won't deal with him.

29:33.520 --> 29:35.520
-Serves you right!
-I… you people…

29:35.600 --> 29:37.960
If it were me,
I wouldn't deal with him either.

29:38.040 --> 29:42.040
If you dare spread rumors
and ruin a woman's name again,

29:42.800 --> 29:44.640
be careful.

29:46.560 --> 29:47.840
My knife has no eyes.

29:48.880 --> 29:49.720
Yes, yes.

30:03.040 --> 30:04.440
-You wretch!
-Landlord!

30:05.680 --> 30:07.440
I… Today I…

30:08.360 --> 30:09.920
WANG'S BRAISED MEATS

30:19.280 --> 30:20.400
Let me see you out.

30:29.680 --> 30:32.560
WANG'S BRAISED MEATS

30:32.640 --> 30:35.040
Is that Fan Changyu?

30:36.600 --> 30:37.440
Exactly.

30:39.920 --> 30:40.800
Interesting.

30:41.320 --> 30:43.360
Turns out she's quite the fiery one.

30:44.600 --> 30:45.760
Let's go.

30:46.280 --> 30:47.120
Let's go.

30:56.160 --> 30:59.040
Your injuries aren't fully healed yet.
Why did you come?

30:59.720 --> 31:00.800
I just came to see.

31:01.320 --> 31:02.960
Heard you went to Wang's.

31:03.040 --> 31:04.240
So I came to take you home.

31:04.920 --> 31:05.840
How did it go?

31:06.520 --> 31:07.960
I hadn't even laid a hand on him.

31:08.040 --> 31:10.800
I just kicked the table
and he nearly fainted.

31:11.600 --> 31:12.520
Then he…

31:15.080 --> 31:16.120
Why do you stop?

31:17.480 --> 31:18.480
You…

31:18.560 --> 31:21.200
Do you think I'm vulgar too?

31:24.080 --> 31:25.200
You wretch!

31:39.680 --> 31:41.080
Those who have enough to eat and wear

31:41.160 --> 31:43.960
can afford to talk
about vulgarity or refinement.

31:44.560 --> 31:46.680
But for those struggling to survive,

31:46.760 --> 31:48.640
no one has the right to judge.

31:53.640 --> 31:56.080
Before, my father wouldn't let me fight
in front of others.

31:57.560 --> 31:58.680
My mother even more so.

31:59.360 --> 32:00.560
She wouldn't let me butcher pigs.

32:01.640 --> 32:03.640
She said if a girl knew such things,

32:03.720 --> 32:04.840
people would laugh at her.

32:06.560 --> 32:09.920
If I married Song Yan,
even if he didn't mind,

32:10.680 --> 32:12.760
others would gossip behind my back.

32:14.320 --> 32:15.680
Later, Father and Mother died.

32:16.960 --> 32:18.120
To make a living,

32:18.760 --> 32:20.600
I had no choice but to butcher pigs.

32:21.520 --> 32:23.680
And even fought
to teach people lessons several times.

32:24.280 --> 32:27.520
Now everyone in town
probably thinks I'm some she-devil.

32:28.880 --> 32:31.040
The gambling house
even sent me an invitation,

32:31.560 --> 32:33.760
saying that if I ever
stopped slaughtering pigs,

32:33.840 --> 32:35.000
I could help them collect debts.

32:37.200 --> 32:38.120
Then go collect debts.

32:39.280 --> 32:40.160
Really?

32:41.480 --> 32:42.800
You're encouraging me to do that?

32:43.400 --> 32:45.360
I'm telling you
not to fear people's gossip.

32:46.760 --> 32:49.840
Rumors cost nothing to spread.

32:50.360 --> 32:52.760
Their harm is great, especially for women.

32:53.480 --> 32:54.680
You have to make them hurt

32:55.520 --> 32:57.160
more than their victims.

32:57.240 --> 32:58.400
That is the only way to cut it off
at the root.

33:02.080 --> 33:04.000
Cut it off at the root?

33:04.080 --> 33:05.520
What does that mean?

33:09.400 --> 33:10.320
Take a guess.

33:11.120 --> 33:12.160
I don't know.

33:13.040 --> 33:15.000
-Just try.
-So what does it mean?

33:15.800 --> 33:18.800
-It means…
-Means what?

33:26.880 --> 33:29.160
Changyu, eat! Zheng, eat!

33:31.280 --> 33:35.400
All this oil and food,
where did it come from?

33:35.480 --> 33:36.640
Father bought them.

33:37.520 --> 33:38.880
Hey, don't talk nonsense.

33:39.400 --> 33:41.120
Ning isn't talking nonsense.

33:41.200 --> 33:43.440
I was surprised too when I saw all this.

33:43.520 --> 33:46.600
The shop assistant said it was silver
your father deposited months ago.

33:46.680 --> 33:48.880
It was all exchanged
for New Year goods and delivered here.

33:49.440 --> 33:51.720
Where would my father get so much money?

33:53.360 --> 33:54.560
They were really from Father?

33:54.640 --> 33:56.960
Yes. That gentleman is called Fan Erniu.

33:57.040 --> 33:59.280
See? How could this be fake?

33:59.360 --> 34:02.640
Now, where would you find a fool
who delivers goods for others for free?

34:04.480 --> 34:05.720
Yan Zheng, isn't that right?

34:07.160 --> 34:08.120
Yes.

34:09.239 --> 34:11.400
It's not much.

34:11.480 --> 34:12.840
Nothing worth mentioning.

34:16.360 --> 34:17.960
Not much?

34:19.199 --> 34:21.320
Changyu, look, there's also this!

34:24.800 --> 34:26.120
Clam ointment?

34:26.199 --> 34:28.760
Food is one thing,
but why buy something so useless?

34:29.840 --> 34:31.679
Which shop? I'll return it.

34:31.760 --> 34:33.040
Don't return it.

34:33.679 --> 34:36.159
Father must have felt sorry
for your chapped hands.

34:36.239 --> 34:37.199
They are for you.

34:37.800 --> 34:41.159
Father wouldn't waste money
on something useless.

34:41.239 --> 34:42.280
I'll return it and buy candy.

34:42.360 --> 34:43.400
Wait.

34:48.719 --> 34:50.000
Once used…

34:51.960 --> 34:53.480
it can't be returned.

34:57.920 --> 35:00.160
-If you like it, take it and use it.
-No.

35:00.240 --> 35:02.480
If you don't want it, why open it?

35:03.840 --> 35:05.800
Once used, it can't be returned.

35:07.680 --> 35:10.960
Silly girl. Your husband cares about you.

35:11.040 --> 35:12.760
He wants you to keep it for yourself.

35:25.400 --> 35:27.120
MARRIAGE

35:50.360 --> 35:51.720
It's already opened.

35:53.240 --> 35:54.680
I'll just use a bit.

36:05.080 --> 36:06.520
Buying such useless things…

36:07.920 --> 36:09.320
What was Father thinking?

36:12.280 --> 36:13.360
Your father

36:14.160 --> 36:15.360
was thinking exactly that.

36:36.640 --> 36:39.880
The trial begins tomorrow.

36:41.360 --> 36:43.280
Do you need me to accompany you?

36:43.960 --> 36:46.720
No, Mr. Zhao and the others will be there.

36:46.800 --> 36:49.120
Your leg is injured.
Kneeling for long won't do you any good.

36:51.480 --> 36:52.960
I've memorized all you taught me.

36:53.480 --> 36:54.440
I'm not afraid.

37:04.400 --> 37:05.680
No knives allowed.

37:08.960 --> 37:11.600
-This is my tool of livelihood.
-Not allowed.

37:20.920 --> 37:23.920
INTEGRITY, PRUDENCE, DILIGENCE

37:28.840 --> 37:30.840
YAMEN

37:32.400 --> 37:33.760
That's right.

37:36.080 --> 37:38.320
Where are Fan Daniu and his wife?

37:39.120 --> 37:40.360
Have they lost track of time?

37:43.320 --> 37:44.680
Those two heartless wretches.

37:44.760 --> 37:46.880
I'd believe they'd even
forget their own parents' names.

37:47.400 --> 37:50.040
But forget fighting over a house?
I don't believe it.

37:51.040 --> 37:52.000
That's true.

37:52.880 --> 37:54.480
Then what are they up to?

37:55.400 --> 37:56.720
They're the plaintiffs!

38:04.800 --> 38:07.640
JUSTICE IS BLIND

38:08.480 --> 38:12.640
-Court is in session.
-Order in court…

38:12.720 --> 38:15.480
Bring forth the plaintiff
and the defendant!

38:15.560 --> 38:16.400
ORDER

38:23.280 --> 38:24.840
Who kneels before the court?

38:24.920 --> 38:26.840
I am Fan Changyu.

38:26.920 --> 38:28.640
I pay my respects, Your Honor.

38:36.480 --> 38:38.560
Where is the plaintiff, Fan Daniu?

38:46.760 --> 38:47.920
Outrageous!

38:48.440 --> 38:50.520
In all my years on the bench,

38:50.600 --> 38:52.840
this is the first time
a plaintiff has failed to appear.

38:56.120 --> 38:57.320
Your Honor, please be calm.

38:57.400 --> 39:00.160
Fan Daniu's continued absence
suggests something may be amiss.

39:00.840 --> 39:03.480
How about sending a constable
to his home to investigate?

39:03.560 --> 39:06.440
That would demonstrate
Your Honor's fairness in this matter.

39:07.560 --> 39:08.520
Granted.

39:09.240 --> 39:10.240
Constable Wang.

39:10.320 --> 39:13.160
Send men to the Fan residence
in East Village at once.

39:13.240 --> 39:14.080
Yes.

39:15.080 --> 39:18.360
-Court is adjourned for now.
-Court adjourned.

39:19.120 --> 39:20.360
-Adjourned?
-What?

39:21.480 --> 39:24.000
-Come. Make way.
-Mr. Wang, what's going on?

39:24.080 --> 39:25.680
It's fine. Come.

39:30.160 --> 39:32.960
Changyu didn't seize Fan Daniu, did she?

39:33.040 --> 39:35.000
Why capture him?

39:35.080 --> 39:37.000
Changyu is already married.

39:37.080 --> 39:39.680
With a case she's bound to win,
why would she risk it?

39:40.280 --> 39:42.760
Besides, she was at home
the whole time last night.

39:42.840 --> 39:44.880
Alright, that sets my mind at ease.

39:48.040 --> 39:51.280
‎YAMEN

39:51.360 --> 39:54.360
JUSTICE IS BLIND

39:54.440 --> 39:57.280
QINGPING COUNTY YAMEN

40:08.520 --> 40:09.720
Court is now in session!

40:09.800 --> 40:13.520
Order in court…

40:13.600 --> 40:16.240
Your Honor, I have taken in
a live-in husband.

40:16.320 --> 40:18.840
By law, I am entitled
to inherit the family house.

40:22.120 --> 40:24.440
We've waited an hour.
We will wait no longer.

40:25.280 --> 40:27.200
Since the plaintiff has failed to appear,

40:27.280 --> 40:30.920
judgment is hereby awarded
to the defendant!

40:31.800 --> 40:33.280
Your Honor!

40:34.760 --> 40:36.040
Your Honor!

40:36.560 --> 40:37.920
Your Honor!

40:41.920 --> 40:46.840
You must uphold justice
for me, Your Honor!

40:50.920 --> 40:52.040
Your Honor!

40:52.720 --> 40:56.040
You must see justice done!

41:05.760 --> 41:07.640
You cursed girl!

41:08.240 --> 41:10.000
To seize this house,

41:10.080 --> 41:12.800
you even killed your own uncle!

43:50.560 --> 43:53.440
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

43:53.520 --> 43:54.440
‎Subtitle translation by: Peng Peng
